<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">ت ي ع:</span> <span class="c2">(التِّيعَةُ)</span> بِالْكَسْرِ بِوَزْنِ الْبِيعَةِ أَرْبَعُونَ مِنَ الْغَنَمِ.<span class="c5"> وَفِي الْحَدِيثِ:</span> <span class="c2">«فِي التِّيعَةِ شَاةٌ»</span> .<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>